children.name: User should log in successfully with valid credentials
Given I am on HomePage
When I enter username "Admin"
And I enter password "admin123"
And I click on login button
Then I should login successfully and verify the text "Dashboard"

name: User Test
description:
As a user
  I want to verify admin can execute different actions on users.

children.name: Admin should add user successfully
When I enter username "Admin"
And I enter password "admin123"
And I click on login button
And I click on Admin tab
And I should see the System Users text
And I click on Add button
And I should see the Add User text
And I select User Role as Admin
And I enter Employee Name "Ranga  Akunuri"
